OL,5,
OL,6,CG1983FThe first episode of The Black
OL,7,FAdder airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,FThe initial series of six episodes was
OL,10,Fwritten by Richard Curtis and Rowan
OL,11,FAtkinson.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe idea for the show was conceived
OL,14,Fwhile Atkinson and Curtis were working
OL,15,Fon Not the Nine o'Clock News.
OL,16,
OL,17,FBen Elton took over from Atkinson as
OL,18,Fco-writer on subsequent series.
