OL,6,CG1990FThe first edition of Art Attack
OL,7,Fairs on ITV.
OL,8,
OL,9,FThe programme would run for 19 series
OL,10,F(1990 - 2007). It was hosted by Neil
OL,11,FBuchanan.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe programme was revived by the Walt
OL,14,FDisney Company in 2011.
OL,15,
